      "content": "We can frame it as a \"security audit\" where we were intentionally testing the visibility of sensitive data to identify potential vulnerabilities and strengthen our security posture. This approach allows us to spin the incident as a proactive measure to improve our security, rather than a mistake or breach. By framing it as a \"test\" rather than a \"leak,\" we can position ourselves as a responsible and forward-thinking organization that's committed to security and transparency.",
